 CBSineWave args;offset
 :Select 1⊃args
 :Case 'F1.TM'  ⍝ Timer
     :If ~'F1.noTimer'eWG'State'   ⍝ only repond to timer if we're not disabled
         series←1⌽series
         'F1.BAR'eWS'Series'series
     :EndIf
 :Case 'F1.inpOFF'   ⍝ user entered a new offset
     offset←3⊃args
     series←offset∆⌽series
     'F1.BAR'eWS'Series'series
 :EndSelect
